# MDC: Generate Module
**Path:** `src/generate/`
**Purpose:** Gemini-powered ad copy generation from resolved briefs.
**Model:** `gemini-1.5-flash` (default) · `gemini-1.5-pro` (quality escalation only)

---

## Files

```
src/generate/
├── __init__.py
├── base.py           — Abstract BaseGenerator interface
