## Test Specification

### `tests/unit/test_generator.py`

```
Interface compliance
- V1Generator is instance of BaseGenerator
- V2Generator.generate() → NotImplementedError
- V3Generator.generate() → NotImplementedError

V1Generator.generate()
- returns Ad with all required fields populated
- Ad.image_url is None (V1 text only)
- Ad.brief_id matches input brief.brief_id
- primary_text length ≤ brief.inferred.ad_length_target
- cta_button value is in VALID_CTA_BUTTONS
- prompt sent to Gemini includes brief.audience
- prompt sent to Gemini includes brief.campaign_goal
- prompt sent to Gemini includes brief.inferred.hook_style
- malformed Gemini JSON response → GenerationError (not raw exception)
- mocked passing Gemini response → parsed correctly into Ad model

V1Generator.regenerate()
- clarity failure → strategy approach is FULL_REWRITE
- cta failure → strategy approach is TARGETED
- emotional_resonance failure → strategy approach is HOOK_REWRITE
- brand_voice failure → strategy approach is TONE_REWRITE
- value_proposition failure → strategy approach is TARGETED
- regeneration prompt includes original primary_text
- regeneration prompt includes failed dimension name
- regeneration prompt includes score for failed dimension
- returned Ad has same brief_id as input Ad
- returned Ad has same id as input Ad (same ad object, new copy)

Prompt construction
- optional brief fields present in prompt when not None
- optional brief fields absent from prompt when None
- FEAR hook style generates different prompt than ASPIRATION hook style
- SOCIAL_PROOF hook prompt includes explicit instruction about proof elements
```

